  "metadata": {
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Locking views in storyboard and XIB files"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before you export localizations, optionally lock the views in your storyboard and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "XIB files so you don’t inadvertently change localizable properties while you’re waiting",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for translations. Use this feature if you want to continue developing your app and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "avoid conflicts when importing localizations later. You can choose a locking level",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that controls the set of editable properties for each view.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Lock-views",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Lock views",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can set the locking level for a single view or for the entire user interface",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "file. By default, views inherit their lock attribute from their parent view, and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "top-level views inherit their lock attribute from the user interface file. If you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "set a view’s lock attribute, it sets the lock attribute for all its descendant views.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To lock a single view, select the user interface file (files with a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": ".storyboard",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": ".xib",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " filename extension) in the Project navigator, then select the view in Interface",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Builder. In the Identity inspector, choose a locking level from the Lock pop-up menu",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "under Document:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Use the parent view’s locking level.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Inherited - ([locking level])",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Don’t lock any properties (make all properties editable).",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Nothing",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Lock all properties.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "All Properties",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Lock localizable properties, such as user-facing text and size.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Localizable Properties",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "Lock non-localizable properties (make user-facing text and size properties editable).",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Non-localizable Properties",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "type": "termList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "locking-views-in-storyboard-and-xib-files-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For example, choose Localizable Properties while waiting for translations from localizers.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "If you import localizations and don’t want to make other changes inadvertently, choose",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Non-localizable Properties.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To lock all views, select the user interface file in the Project navigator, then",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "choose a locking level from the Editor > Localization Locking menu.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Unlock-views",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Unlock views",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To unlock all views after you import localizations, select the user interface file",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in the Project navigator, then choose Editor > Localization Locking > Reset Locking",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Controls. To prevent any edits in a user interface file that would impact localized",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "strings files, choose Editor > Localization Locking > Reset Locking Controls and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "then choose Editor > Localization Locking > Localizable Properties.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
